Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.34,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}如伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:16.97,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}那份纯真的勇气如今已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:19.32,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:22.69,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}将那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:29.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:37.21,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}寻找答案 却陷入迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:44.61,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}若能得知 答案的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:51.18,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}一切将化作崭新的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:59.42,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:01.33,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:07.53,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}总有一天会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:13.63,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:18.77,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:22.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:25.53,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}便能迎着清风 乱了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:29.52,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}勇往直前吧
