Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:34.50,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}相互触碰之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:41.43,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻 你在想着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:47.16,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隔着玻璃晃过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.06,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那忧伤的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:55.40,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}距离那么近 却无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:59.87,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}积累种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.72,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}逃避着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:10.74,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那时几近崩溃的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.09,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻仿佛已能面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:15.77,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Love in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:18.20,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}打开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:21.68,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}前往有你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:28.75,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}告诉你这份焦灼已久的心情
