Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然停了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊 还用怀表？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特别的日子 所以找出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别的日子…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上有钟表店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止当我们这儿是孤岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君还没去过商店街那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在今天之内修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我今天就带你上街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤岛的街啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你们俩玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来约会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 那怀表为什么一定要今天修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有点原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像木头棒子似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是防身棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防身棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是碰到毒蛇就用那棒子吓走它免得被咬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还真有孤岛风范
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 居高临下的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 竟然有剧场还有新潮的书店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想买色情杂志的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我在外面等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何收获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱岛上秩序的人 决不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衬衫 蛮适合须方的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 是须方君的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 须方君不喜欢过生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「须方」是进藤家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每代生就带有印记的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能取的特别的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君知道自己的身世和素体的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是5年前的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后 他好像就很讨厌自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方也能驾驶素体？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君的 有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn那些是战士的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继承的是巫女的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 进藤家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君继承的是王的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量大概是这个星球最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的素体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那台素体多半坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是不能驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体虽然不能动 却可以驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驭者将会获得强力的第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一阶段…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子夫人的背部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姿色和商业才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是第一阶段的力量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由驯化产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在零时空间以外也能使用的素体之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是第一阶段的定义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不一定是超常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社会上突然大获成功的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是将第一阶段的力量据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能如果被社会认同也算幸福的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异能的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只会让持有者遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巫女的我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方同学想离开是可以离开岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了避免那强大的力量在外部使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君也被禁止离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这孤岛所困
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方拥有什么力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然拥有印记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是须方君没有驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化王之素体的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下记录的几乎所有驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在使用了被称为王之柱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强力第一阶段力量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入深沉的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也没有醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷茶是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个轻浮女和那外乡人发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会失去巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能坐视计划继续被拖延了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还无法控制自己的第一阶段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰别人谈恋爱就太不解风情了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言是重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和须方君 从小相识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在这里的皆水神社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了封印巫女的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知命中注定无法离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却能坚持到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是因为有背负着同样命运的须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 总是随身携带着小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么带着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直害怕 不敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候须方君生日宴会上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他戴着我送的玻璃珠项链
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提多高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是他的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能对他说生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年在其他日子 找其他理由送出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你们俩玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的生日成为讨厌的纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想利用拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他庆祝生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这座岛上要有素体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要生在这岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去把礼物交给须方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷今天不见任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己一个人关在道场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方在不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有须方君的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这是我给须方的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 也是给自己的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿唱首歌好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险又漆黑的夜海上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆手持鱼叉 发起挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无法用语言叙述的激烈战斗过后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死乌贼大王的萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于获得了那青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 没有战斗场景描写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼大王的青色血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瓶中煌煌生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了夜色的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满神秘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着这瓶青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆得以晋见国王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王大人 这是约定的青色血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王激动得浑身发抖 接过瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口喝下了那瓶青色液体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被施以不老不死的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来结束他永恒人生的唯一解药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜入眠后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便也不会再次醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意料的剧情展开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果汁 不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 萨姆怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险仍在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊人胃口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游弋吧 美人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等前来相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水大人请隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子躲好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防身棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 温蒂尼（Ondine）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 犯规也得有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪快 银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 温蒂尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让它做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水巫女也在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美人鱼自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深层意识的暴走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's a pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柱！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王之柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 须方君
